   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Seventy-nine THERE IS ONE GOD AND ONE MEDIATOR Scripture: 1 Tim 2:5 There is only one God As there cannot be two heads in a household or two kings in a nation, so there cannot be two Gods in the universe.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>This God is the Creator and the Ruler of the universe.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>He is also the Savior of mankind.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>There is only one mediator In human history there have been many wise and famous men, yet not one has claimed to be, nor has been recognized as, a mediator between God and man.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Only Jesus Christ said that He is the mediator between God and man.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>The Bible says that He is the one, the only mediator.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>How Jesus became the mediator He was God coming as man.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>He had both divinity and humanity, so He was qualified to be the mediator between God and man.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>He was crucified and His blood was shed for our sins to remove the hindrance between God and man.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>So He became the mediator between God and man.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>He resurrected and imparted His life to man so that man could have God s life and be one with God.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>Through this process He became the mediator between God and man.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>How to receive Jesus as your mediator</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Develop this point.</S>
   </TEXT>
